## 1. Agreement to Terms

By providing your phone number and consenting to receive SMS messages from Polly-App, you agree to these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree, do not provide your phone number or consent to receive messages.

## 2. SMS Messaging Service

Polly-App provides an SMS notification service for use in educational and organizational settings. Messages may include reminders, alerts, updates, or other notifications sent on behalf of an authorized organization.

## 3. Consent

By enrolling in the SMS service, you consent to receive text messages from Polly-App at the phone number you provided. Consent is not a condition of any purchase or service.

## 4. Message Frequency

Message frequency varies depending on the needs of the organization sending notifications. You may receive multiple messages per day during active notification periods.

## 5. Message and Data Rates

**Message and data rates may apply.** You are responsible for any fees charged by your mobile carrier for sending or receiving SMS messages.

## 6. Opt-Out

You may opt out of receiving SMS messages at any time by replying **STOP** to any message. You will receive a confirmation message and no further messages will be sent. To re-enroll, reply **START**.

## 7. Help

For help, reply **HELP** to any message or contact us at abrahamborg@gmail.com.

## 8. Supported Carriers

Polly-App supports all major US mobile carriers. Carrier availability is not guaranteed in all areas.

## 9. Limitation of Liability

Polly-App is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We are not liable for any delays, failures, or errors in SMS delivery caused by mobile carriers or other third-party services.

## 10. Authorized Use

This service is intended for use by authorized organizations and their designated recipients only. Unauthorized use is prohibited.

